channel.title: Version 5.1 :: Hugo Relearn Theme
channel.description: 5.1.0 (2022-07-15) Hugo 0.95.0 0.95.0 This release requires a newer Hugo version. Change Change Because the print preview URLs were non deterministic for normal pages in comparison to page bundles, this is now changed. Each print preview is now accessible by adding a index.print.html to the default URL.
